{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerWhatsappNumber:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"number","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number in E.164 international format.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"number"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates a WhatsApp number with the current device for WhatsApp Business API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"messaging campaigns. This enables rich messaging with images, documents, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interactive buttons through WhatsApp."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Must be a valid WhatsApp-enabled number"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register WhatsApp during communication preferences setup:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class CommunicationPreferencesManager {","","    struct Preferences {","        var pushEnabled: Bool","        var smsEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappEnabled: Bool","        var whatsappNumber: String?","    }","","    func savePreferences(_ preferences: Preferences) {","        \/\/ Register WhatsApp if user opted in and provided number","        if preferences.whatsappEnabled, let number = preferences.whatsappNumber {","            let normalizedNumber = normalizePhoneNumber(number)","            Pushwoosh.configure.registerWhatsappNumber(normalizedNumber)","        }","","        \/\/ Update channel preferences tags","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"channel_push\": preferences.pushEnabled,","            \"channel_sms\": preferences.smsEnabled,","            \"channel_whatsapp\": preferences.whatsappEnabled","        ])","    }","","    private func normalizePhoneNumber(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.filter { $0.isNumber }","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+\\(digits)\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerwhatsappnumber:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers a WhatsApp number for WhatsApp Business messaging."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerWhatsappNumber:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerWhatsappNumber:"}],"title":"registerWhatsappNumber:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerWhatsappNumber:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerWhatsappNumber:"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"mino